{
  "text": "Having identified the free energy corresponding to the non-condensed part of the fluid, we provide the statistical mechanical description for this non-condensate phase characterized by \u2126 N in Eq. [CITATION_1] . To achieve that, first we obtain the thermodynamic relations for the noncondensed part of the fluid. The free energy \u2126 N (16) satisfies the thermodynamic relation,",
