    "121109807": {
      "title": "Curvature squared terms and string theories",
      "abstract": "Abstract The compatibility between the presence of curvature squared terms and the absence of ghost particles in the low energy limits of string theories is established. The lagrangian \u0283\u221ag d D \u00d7(R \u03bc\u03bd\u03f1\u03c3 R \u03bc\u03bd\u03f1\u03c3 \u22124R \u03bc\u03bd R \u03bc\u03bd +R 2 ) leads to ghost-free nontrivial gravitational self-interactions for dimensions higher than four."
    }
  }
